-- Mitsubishi Motors First-Half Loss Narrows to $60 Million on Sales Gain
-- B y   T a k e h i k o   K u m a k u r a
-- 2010-10-22T06:06:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/mitsubishi-motors-first-half-loss-narrows-to-60-million-on-sales-gain.html
Mitsubishi Motors Corp. said its
first-half loss narrowed to 4.9 billion yen ($60 million) from
36.4 billion yen a year earlier after sales gained. The company
had forecast a 9 billion yen loss for the period. It announced
the figures in a statement to the Tokyo Stock Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Takehiko Kumakura in Tokyo at 
 tkumakura@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
